pros:
1. The office tools used for WFH are diverse and very efficient;
2. Many colleagues have overseas study background or overseas work experiencce and they are culturally open and inclusive;
3. Anyone who works in the company just needs to focus on getting things done and so the way of collaboration is direct and effective.

cons:
1. Working overtime is quite often and it somehow keeps you from WLB;
2. Sometimes there could be more people than work and it creates tension and competitions even within the same team. 
3. The career ladder is not crystal clear to all employees.

pros:
Basically working for Tiktok, so the atmosphere is dynamic, inclusive; 
International scope;
Chances to interact with very experienced, insightful people
